<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-04-1476 </DOCNO><TEXT>On the subject of energy policy, mention should also be made of the publicationand presentation of the Renewable Energy Plan (PER) and the continueddiscussions with the electricity industry on rationalisation of theirfinancial structure. The renewable energy plan, drawn up in responseto a resolution from Parliament in connection with the 1983 NationalEnergy Plan, considers the following resources: energy, wind, biomass,minihydro-electric power stations, atmospheric thermal energy; geothermalenergy. 10 tabs., 7 figs.</TEXT></DOC>